                <button class="legacyIssueTab is-active" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="legacy-issue-a" id="legacy-issue-tab-a" data-legacy-tab="legacy-issue-a">A. Entry confusion</button>
                <button class="legacyIssueTab" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="legacy-issue-b" id="legacy-issue-tab-b" data-legacy-tab="legacy-issue-b">B. Missing provider context</button>
                <button class="legacyIssueTab" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="legacy-issue-c" id="legacy-issue-tab-c" data-legacy-tab="legacy-issue-c">C. Unclear next action</button>
                <button class="legacyIssueTab" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="legacy-issue-d" id="legacy-issue-tab-d" data-legacy-tab="legacy-issue-d">D. Repetitive checkout flow</button>
              </div>

              <div class="legacyIssuePanels">
                <article class="legacyIssuePanel is-active" id="legacy-issue-a" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="legacy-issue-tab-a" data-legacy-panel>
                  <img class="modal-target card2026 legacyIssueImg" src="legacy_pre_entry.png" alt="Legacy Vrbo entry added friction before shopping" data-modal-gallery="legacy-issue-carousel">
                  <div class="legacyIssueCopy">
                    <div class="marginLeft">
                      <ul class="listCircle">
                        <li>Blank loading state created uncertainty</li>
                        <li>Multiple overlays competed for attention</li>
                        <li>Chat blocking the primary CTA</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                </article>

                <article class="legacyIssuePanel" id="legacy-issue-b" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="legacy-issue-tab-b" data-legacy-panel hidden>
                  <img class="modal-target card2026 legacyIssueImg" src="legacy_shop_placeholder_items.png" alt="    Legacy shopping with generic products and pricing" data-modal-gallery="legacy-issue-carousel">

                  <div class="legacyIssueCopy">
                    <div class="marginLeft">
                      <ul class="listCircle">
                        <li>Users added items before selecting a provider</li>
                        <li>Starting prices masked provider-dependent pricing</li>
                        <li>Generic product details lacked provider context</li>
                        <li>Shopping didn’t naturally transition to provider selection</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </article>

                <article class="legacyIssuePanel" id="legacy-issue-c" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="legacy-issue-tab-c" data-legacy-panel hidden>
                  <img class="modal-target card2026 legacyIssueImg" src="legacy_provider_selection.png" alt="    Legacy provider selection lacked clear guidance" data-modal-gallery="legacy-issue-carousel">

                  <div class="legacyIssueCopy">
                    <div class="marginLeft">
                      <ul class="listCircle">
                        <li>Add-to-cart feedback suggested completion</li>
                        <li>CTA hierarchy favored continued browsing</li>
                        <li>Provider selection wasn’t presented as the next required step</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </article>

                <article class="legacyIssuePanel" id="legacy-issue-d" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="legacy-issue-tab-d" data-legacy-panel hidden>
                  <img class="modal-target card2026 legacyIssueImg" src="legacy_precheckout.png" alt="Legacy flow with repeated checkout states" data-modal-gallery="legacy-issue-carousel">

                  <div class="legacyIssueCopy">
                    <div class="marginLeft">
                      <ul class="listCircle">
                        <li>Checkout and add-ons created repetitive loops</li>
                        <li>Competing CTAs blurred the next step</li>
                        <li>Users reached checkout before they were ready</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </article>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <div class="marginLeft">
              <ul class="listCircle">
                <li><span class="fontWeight400">Entry:</span> unclear context and trust (“Where am I?”)</li>
                <li><span class="fontWeight400">Shopping:</span> misleading progress (“This feels like a real cart”)</li>
                <li><span class="fontWeight400">Commitment:</span> missing decision moment (“I haven’t actually chosen a provider”)</li>
                <li><span class="fontWeight400">Pre-checkout:</span> redundant flow (“Why am I doing this again?”)</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="spacingXSmall"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <div class="specialCaseStudyTxt">
              <h5>Users do not need to understand how this marketplace works. They may just want to rent a crib.</h5>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wrapper">


      <div class="spacingXLarge"></div>

      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <div class="blankHXXS"></div>
            <h1 class="fontWeight400">Marketplace mental model mismatch</h1>
            <h4>These issues weren’t independent usability problems. They all stemmed from a mismatch between the user’s mental model and the marketplace architecture.</h4>




          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="spacingXLarge"></div>

      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--cols-2 u-textCenter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <h4 class="fontWeight400">Traveler mindset</h4>
            <div class="spacingMedium"></div>

            <img class="" src="diagram_traveler.svg" alt="Vrbo mobile vs non-Vrbo mobile">




          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <h4 class="fontWeight400">Marketplace workflow</h4>
            <div class="spacingMedium"></div>

            <img class="" src="diagram_marketplace.svg" alt="Vrbo mobile vs Vrbo web">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
    <div class="spacingMedium"></div>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
